'''Tatyana Alexandra Eugenie Yassukovich''' ([[April]], [[1962]]) is an actress. The daughter of businessman Stanislas Yassukovich, she spent her school days in Switzerland, and as such has become fluent in English, French, German and Italian. So far, her biggest role is that of the storyteller in ''[[wikipedia:Chocolat (2000 film)|Chocolat]]''.
